{"tid":770102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平被打傷","createTime":"2018-08-06T17:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T04:20:07.000Z","uid":100276,"like":448,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"ff2253c8791c2d6294bcc1f1bac1d81b26dac332","tid":770102,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T17:58:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/219238/反了-杭州貌似習近平的士司機被打傷-新聞片段遭河蟹\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C%2F219238%2F%E5%8F%8D%E4%BA%86-%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7%9E%E8%B2%8C%E4%BC%BC%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93%E5%82%B7-%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E9%81%AD%E6%B2%B3%E8%9F%B9&d=8pQux4UZmuDDUh%2BBBDQEekbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=83f1109d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/219238/反了-杭州貌似習近平的士司機被打傷-新聞片段遭河蟹</a><br />\n杭州一名的士司機近日不幸遇上「霸王」乘客拒付車資，更被打傷，事件被媒體報道後，網民卻錯重點，沒人關心司機情況，只紛紛稱其樣子與國家主席習近平很相似。一單普通民生新聞因而被瘋傳，沒料網民反應太熱烈，連新聞片也遭「河蟹」下架，惟醒目網民早已截圖繼續廣傳，令事件成為熱話。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/07/015600_f05fa51695dc207d0a662362d24556d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F07%2F015600_f05fa51695dc207d0a662362d24556d9.png&h=0998a78d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事件被傳媒報道後，羅姓司機受訪的畫面引起內地網民熱議，不少人笑指羅的樣子與國家主席習近平很相似，留言笑稱「難道是習皇帝去民間探訪？」、「長這樣可去當替身吧」，亦有大膽網民戲稱「與錢無關，只因長相」，笑指「真的打不了，只能打假的」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞片段被網民瘋傳後，原片已遭下架，但不少網民早已截圖，繼續把事件當笑料與親朋分享，縱使片段被河蟹，內地討論區仍持續流傳片段截圖，熱潮未見減退。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/07/015744_840f2cf0034cb47d9e6785ac491ea6ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F07%2F015744_840f2cf0034cb47d9e6785ac491ea6ae.png&h=7e1954df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9389767eaff9af12d79f36078725e7a207bf4be","tid":770102,"uid":28765,"like":628,"dislike":2,"score":626,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T18:00:18.000Z","msg":"許多網友認為該名司機的長相，與中國領導人習近平極為神似，紛紛留言指出「這長相沒有把他掛在歪脖子樹上已經不錯啦」、<span style=\"color: red;\">「長這個B樣我也想給他2拳」</span>、「冤有頭債有主」、「不打可惜」、「是習總放他出宮挨打平息民憤的，有替身，真好」、「A貨昏君維尼帝」"},{"pid":"a9bb0387fabba212770fea332919379585769eb1","tid":770102,"uid":198652,"like":141,"dislike":1,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T18:00:21.000Z","msg":"刁種都敢打 反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5646c22eeaf457360c4ac4d04c6cf7addd0a208e","tid":770102,"uid":89530,"like":147,"dislike":2,"score":145,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T18:00:48.000Z","msg":"好撚慘，俾人打完，遲啲仲要被失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06a02f91ae3e05e84310b090e6f50b3dfecce00","tid":770102,"uid":39698,"like":96,"dislike":3,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T18:11:38.000Z","msg":"尋秦記林峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722a05745e926ce9783acf834dfe4ad42ee135aa","tid":770102,"uid":59511,"like":384,"dislike":2,"score":382,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T18:15:53.000Z","msg":"衛訊夠唔夠薑請佢拍廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c535dd8e26f9a6c4669d71b3df6f175b95952d","tid":770102,"uid":294,"like":62,"dislike":3,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T18:17:44.000Z","msg":"睇得出好多中國人都反共"},{"pid":"5f52d8de7ae075e93046ce88e3d101ed8d703831","tid":770102,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"722a05745e926ce9783acf834dfe4ad42ee135aa","tid":770102,"uid":59511,"like":384,"dislike":2,"score":382,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T18:15:53.000Z","msg":"衛訊夠唔夠薑請佢拍廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T18:18:09.000Z","msg":"Happy birthday to me <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im